                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The hobgoblins draw their shortbows, then launch a ranged attack in the form of a volley. This volley is a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 60 feet that deals @Damage[4d6[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage with a @Check[reflex|dc:25|basic|options:area-effect] save. When the regiment is reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
